<item>
            <title>[LU-5893] Kernel update [RHEL7 3.10.0-123.9.3.el7]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5893</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Previously, a use-after-free bug in the Common Block IO controller cgroup&lt;br/&gt;
interface code could result in a kernel panic on systems using the blkio&lt;br/&gt;
subsystem. An upstream patch that fixes this bug has been backported to the&lt;br/&gt;
kernel, and the kernel no longer crashes when working with blkio cgroups.&lt;br/&gt;
(BZ#1158313)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
